BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2027-spring-term-start@example.ecko
DTSTAMP:20260531T120000Z
SUMMARY:Spring Term Begins
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270105
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270106
LOCATION:Whole School
DESCRIPTION:Pupils return to school for the start of the spring term. Gates open from 8:30am.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2027-year-6-residential@example.ecko
DTSTAMP:20260531T120000Z
SUMMARY:Year 6 Residential Trip
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270315
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270318
LOCATION:Oakridge Outdoor Learning Centre
DESCRIPTION:Year 6 pupils will spend three days taking part in outdoor learning activities. Full kit list and medical forms will be sent to families in advance.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2027-parent-consultation-evening@example.ecko
DTSTAMP:20260531T120000Z
SUMMARY:Parent Consultation Evening
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/London:20270420T153000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/London:20270420T190000
LOCATION:School Hall and Classrooms
DESCRIPTION:Appointments with class teachers to discuss pupil progress. Booking details will be shared through the school office.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2027-sports-day@example.ecko
DTSTAMP:20260531T120000Z
SUMMARY:Whole School Sports Day
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/London:20270618T093000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/London:20270618T143000
LOCATION:School Field
DESCRIPTION:Families are invited to join us for races\, team games and a picnic lunch. Please ensure pupils bring a water bottle\, sun hat and suitable PE kit.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2027-autumn-half-term@example.ecko
DTSTAMP:20260531T120000Z
SUMMARY:Autumn Half Term Holiday
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20271025
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20271030
LOCATION:School Closed
DESCRIPTION:The school will be closed for the autumn half term break. Pupils return on Monday 1 November 2027.
END:VEVENT
